MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt15Intro:
	.string "Hey. Me again. Do you happen to know\n"
	.string "VYRAL’s training routine?\p"
	.string "I bet it’s really intense. Do you\n"
	.string "think she could bench press me.$"

